title: Should QuickSwap Pay Liquidity Mining Rewards in dQUICK Instead of QUICK?
body:
Recently, the QuickSwap community has been talking about the DEX taking measures to reduce sell pressure on QUICK. We're wondering what our community thinks of this idea:
 
Should we start rewarding in dQUICK instead of QUICK?

If this proposal were to pass:

* QUICK earned from providing liquidity would be automatically staked to begin earning interest from trading fees immediately.
* Those who chose to would still be able to withdraw it and deposit in compound pools, but the default starting point would be staked in the Dragon’s Lair.
* Earned QUICK would compound automatically.
